                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.51/103.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Vice
                        Consul <persName type="to">Stadden</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-01-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 9, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>At request French Ambassador use good offices to secure release steamer <hi
                        rend="italic">Korrigan II</hi> reported captured at Manzanillo said to
                    belong to French Boleo Company.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
